    },
    {
      "startSeconds": 6.84,
      "endSeconds": 7.68,
      "text": "I picked it up."
    },
    {
      "startSeconds": 7.68,
      "endSeconds": 9.4,
      "text": "The screen said: **Mom**."
    },
    {
      "startSeconds": 9.4,
      "endSeconds": 11.92,
      "text": "I almost didn’t answer. But something felt wrong."
    },
    {
      "startSeconds": 11.92,
      "endSeconds": 12.88,
      "text": "So I swiped."
    },
    {
      "startSeconds": 12.88,
      "endSeconds": 15.96,
      "text": "Before I could speak, a woman whispered, “Don’t turn around.”"
    },
    {
      "startSeconds": 15.96,
      "endSeconds": 17.96,
      "text": "My stomach dropped. I froze."
    },
    {
      "startSeconds": 17.96,
      "endSeconds": 21.4,
      "text": "Then I heard it. Footsteps behind me. Slow. One step. Then another."
    },
    {
      "startSeconds": 21.4,
      "endSeconds": 26.04,
      "text": "The woman on the phone started crying. 'Please,' she said. 'He already has my son.'"
    },
    {
      "startSeconds": 26.04,
      "endSeconds": 27.32,
      "text": "I turned anyway."
    },
    {
      "startSeconds": 27.32,
      "endSeconds": 31.76,
      "text": "And standing under the only broken streetlight… was a little boy. Holding my exact same phone."
    },
    {
      "startSeconds": 31.76,
      "endSeconds": 32.96,
      "text": "And it was ringing too."
    }
  ],
